<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB07815</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT REGULATING THE PLANNING, DESIGN, CONSTRUCTION, OCCUPANCY, AND MAINTENANCE OF BUILDINGS, ENACTING A NEW BUILDING ACT, REPEALING PRESIDENTIAL DECREE NO. 1096, AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Seeks to provide for the effective regulation of planning, design, construction, occupancy, and maintenance of buildings and structures, the establishment of a permitting process based on their classifications, and the setting of reference standards and; promote the accountability of stakeholders in ensuring enforcement of and compliance of this Act. </td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ALIAS NAME : “New Philippine Building Act.” </td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>TAN, ANGELINA &quot;HELEN&quot; D.L. M.D.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-05-30</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Sy-Alvarado (000 2018-08-07)</td><td>2. Nieto (000 2019-01-30)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON PUBLIC WORKS AND HIGHWAYS ON 2018-07-30</td></tr></table>